// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1077 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b8e1a350-28c8-5369-8e75-b050800925fd

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
